{"about_the_game":"<strong>We all love soccer \u2013 but how badly do you want to win?</strong><br><br>FootLOL is the craziest soccer management game you have ever played! Use mines, aliens, cows, guns and other crazy cheats to decimate the opposing team and protect your players. Play against your friends or AI opponents!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/263740/extras/FootLOL_features_2.gif?t=1729030007\" /><br><br>As the manager, you\u2019ll take your team through a few training matches on Earth before being unleashed on new planets. During you trip to the stars, you\u2019ll unlock new gadgets, improve your players\u2019 performance, as well as buy new kits and hats for them to wear.<br><br>Opponents often use the same tricks you do, so it\u2019s not as simple as knocking the ball in the back of the net. You\u2019ll also need to fulfil the various head-scratching conditions for each level! Thankfully, non-stop action, funny characters and the best arsenal seen in a football game ever are at your service.<br><br>Once you\u2019ve finished FootLOL\u2019s tournament mode, you can play against the computer or go online for gripping multiplayer matches. <br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Four planets, each with several types of playing field<br></li><li>Multiplayer<br></li><li>Hilarious soccer chaos<br></li><li>Highly customizable characters and teams<br></li><li>Sixty levels<br></li><li>Crazy abilities and tools</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Invasion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/263740/b3f73c9fd441240940ee811bb7c4e6b11542b171.jpg"},{"name":"Moo","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/263740/17d1f97d6d59d189061e858ddecc09c10e1ef4b1.jpg"},{"name":"Veteran","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/263740/97